## ğŸ› ï¸ Tech Stack

- **GUI**: tkinter + ttkthemes (modern Arc theme)
- **Screen Capture**: PIL ImageGrab
- **Video Processing**: OpenCV
- **Databases**: SQLite + ChromaDB (vector search)
- **AI Models**: Ollama (local MLLM)
- **Language**: Python 3.8+

